-online.com/shiogama_odenkan_lp.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"hoverimg\" src=\"/images/od_banner.png\" width=\"205\" alt=\"かきの旨味だし塩竈おでん缶6缶セット 非常食に最適！\" /></a></div>\n  <!--\n  <div style=\"margin-top:5px;\"><a href=\"https://www.abezen-online.com/shiogama_beer_lp.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"hoverimg\" src=\"/images/beer_banner.jpg\" width=\"205\" alt=\"塩竈の海に乾杯！海の幸によく合う塩竈ビール\" /></a></div>\n-->\n </div><!--/#contents_left-->\n\n <div id=\"ll_contents_right\">\n \n\t\t  <h1>採用情報</h1>\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"aim_box\">\r\n  \r\n  \t<table class=\"recruit_table\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n    \t<tr>\r\n        \t<th>初任給</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">18万400円～</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>諸手当</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">通勤費実費支給（上限20,000円）</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>昇給</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">年1回（8月）</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>賞与</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">年2回（業績による）</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>休日休暇</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">年間110日（日・祝日・年末年始・その他）<br />1年単位変形労働時間制</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>勤務地</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">塩釜市</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>勤務時間</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">8:00～17:00</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>教育制度</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">新入社員研修<br />食品衛生管理研修<br />その他OJT、社内外研修</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th rowspan=\"2\">採用実績校</th>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_blue\">新卒</td>\r\n            <td colspan=\"6\">石巻専修大学、岩手大学、北里大学、尚絅学院大学、東海大学、<br />東北学院大学、東京農工大学、宮城大学、明治学院大学</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_orange\">中途</td>\r\n            <td colspan=\"6\">駒澤大学、仙台大学、拓殖大学、千葉商科大学、東北学院大学、<br />東北福祉大学、明治学院大学</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th rowspan=\"4\">採用実績校</th>\r\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"recruit_table_blue\">新卒</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2019年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2018年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2017年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2016年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2015年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_blue recruit_table_date\">2014年</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">2</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">  </td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"recruit_table_orange\">中途</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2019年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2018年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2017年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2016年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2015年</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date_orange recruit_table_date\">2014年</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">2</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">1</td>\r\n            <td class=\"recruit_table_date\">　</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>募集職種</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">製造職(生産管理)　営業職　スタッフ職(品質管理・商品開発)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>募集人員</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">未定</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>募集学科</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">全学部全学科</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>提出書類</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">履歴書　健康診断書　成績証明書　卒業見込証明書</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>選考方法</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">面接　筆記試験</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        \r\n        <tr>\r\n        \t<th>資格</th>\r\n            <td colspan=\"7\">不問</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n    </table>\r\n  \r\n  </div><!--/.aim_box-->\r\n  \r\n  <p class=\"recruit_arrow\"><img src=\"/images/recruit_arrow_bg.jpg\" width=\"348\" height=\"49\" /></p>\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  <div class=\"aim_box\">\r\n  \t<h2 class=\"quality_h2\">採用に関するお問い合わせはこちら</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <p class=\"quality_banner\"><img src=\"/images/recruit_img1.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"61\" alt=\"お電話でのお問い合わせ\" /></p>\r\n    <p class=\"quality_banner\"><a href=\"https://abezen.co.jp/contact-index/\"><img class=\"hoverimg\" src=\"/images/recruit_img3.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"61\" alt=\"Webからのお問い合わせ\" /></a></p>\r\n    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n  </div><!--/.aim_box-->\r\n    \n </div><!--/#contents_right-->\n <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n \n <p class=\"to_pagetop\"><img src=\"/images/to_pagetop.jpg\" width=\"140\" height=\"23\" alt=\"ページの上部に戻る\" /></p>\n\n</div><!--/#ll_in_contents-->\n</div><!--contents-->\n\n\t<div id=\"footer_link\">\r\n\r\n <ul style=\"width:470px; margin:0 auto;\">\r\n  <!--<li><a href=\"\"><img class=\"hoverimg\" src=\"/images/footer_link_privacy.jpg\" width=\"148\" height=\"15\" alt=\"プライバシーポリシー\" /></a></li>-->\r\n  <!--<li><a href=\"\"><img class=\"hoverimg\" src=\"/images/footer_link_law.jpg\" width=